Objective:
Create users, groups, and permissions

Steps:
# Create group
sudo groupadd devops

# Create users
sudo useradd -m user1
sudo useradd -m user2

# Set password
sudo passwd user1
sudo passwd user2

# Add users to group
sudo usermod -aG devops user1
sudo usermod -aG devops user2

Set Shared Folder:
sudo mkdir /project
sudo chown :devops /project
sudo chmod 770 /project
